1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:02,002
<i>Lucas.</i>

2
00:00:02,085 --> 00:00:05,588
<i>We're here in the basement's</i>
<i>mechanical room.</i>

3
00:00:05,672 --> 00:00:07,173
<i>The tunnel's almost done.</i>

4
00:00:07,257 --> 00:00:08,550
<i>- Let's meet at--</i>
- [CABRAL]<i> Hello.</i>

5
00:00:09,926 --> 00:00:11,761
<i>This is General Cabral.</i>

6
00:00:11,845 --> 00:00:13,888
<i>The police know our location.</i>

7
00:00:14,764 --> 00:00:16,057
<i>Detonate it!</i>

8
00:00:16,141 --> 00:00:17,475
[LUCAS] <i>Blow it up!</i>

9
00:00:17,559 --> 00:00:19,352
[MINNIE SCREAMS, MEN GROAN]

10
00:00:19,436 --> 00:00:22,897
[CABRAL] <i>Areza, they're in the basement.</i>
<i>In the mechanical room. Alert all units!</i>

11
00:00:22,981 --> 00:00:23,815
[AREZA] <i>Yes, sir.</i>

12
00:00:23,898 --> 00:00:27,485
[EMIL]<i> Engineer!</i>
<i>Check if the tunnel is passable.</i>

13
00:00:27,569 --> 00:00:29,696
[MIKE] <i>There's an opening</i>
<i>leading to the old sewage line.</i>

14
00:00:29,779 --> 00:00:33,616
<i>But as I warned you beforehand, the walls</i>
<i>and the upper section are damaged.</i>

15
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:36,661
<i>The temporary frames</i>
<i>and posts are also on fire.</i>

16
00:00:36,745 --> 00:00:39,956
<i>So if I were you, I'd hurry, immediately.</i>

17
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:43,001
<i>Get the engineer's family.</i>
<i>We still need them!</i>

18
00:00:43,585 --> 00:00:44,919
[GUNSHOT, FREDO GROANS]

19
00:00:45,003 --> 00:00:46,504
- [DADO]<i> Boss Emil!</i>
<i>- Put your guns down!</i>

20
00:00:46,588 --> 00:00:48,673
- [MIKE] <i>Minnie! Minnie, run now!</i>
- [MINNIE] <i>Mike!</i>

21
00:00:48,757 --> 00:00:53,136
<i>Run! Hurry!</i>
<i>Don't touch my family, or I'll kill him!</i>

22
00:00:53,219 --> 00:00:56,473
<i>You've got nowhere left to run, Ma.</i>
<i>Turn yourself in.</i>

23
00:00:56,556 --> 00:01:00,727
<i>Let's start over!</i>
<i>You, me, and your father.</i>

24
00:01:00,810 --> 00:01:02,729
<i>Do you want us to be criminals?!</i>

25
00:01:02,812 --> 00:01:05,523
- [GRETA COUGHS]
<i>- Ma. Ma!</i>

26
00:01:06,232 --> 00:01:08,234
- [EMIL GROWLS]
- [GUN CLICKS]

27
00:01:08,318 --> 00:01:09,611
[GUNSHOT]

28
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:14,699
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

29
00:01:15,366 --> 00:01:18,411
[DADO] <i>Boss, I got this.</i>
<i>You should leave now.</i>

30
00:01:22,749 --> 00:01:23,917
[ECHOING BOOM]

31
00:01:28,463 --> 00:01:32,342
[MEN COUGHING]

32
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:35,637
- Boss, we're here.
- Go on, keep moving.

33
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:39,057
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

34
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:41,976
Ow! [EMIL GROANS]

35
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,645
Get inside!

36
00:01:43,728 --> 00:01:44,854
[UNINTELLIGIBLE SHOUTING]

37
00:01:46,147 --> 00:01:47,106
Dado!

38
00:01:47,190 --> 00:01:48,608
[LUCAS SCREAMING]

39
00:01:48,691 --> 00:01:52,237
- Let's go! Get inside!
- Let's go! Dado!

40
00:01:52,737 --> 00:01:53,905
[COUGHING]

41
00:01:53,988 --> 00:01:59,911
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

42
00:02:02,372 --> 00:02:04,624
[GRUNTING]

43
00:02:05,625 --> 00:02:08,336
[FIRE ALARM BEEPING]

44
00:02:08,419 --> 00:02:09,420
[COUGHING]

45
00:02:09,504 --> 00:02:11,339
Go, baby. Go.

46
00:02:11,422 --> 00:02:18,388
[COUGHING]

47
00:02:18,471 --> 00:02:20,306
[GROANS, COUGHS]

48
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:22,934
Go, baby. Go. Go.

49
00:02:23,017 --> 00:02:25,728
[MINNIE BREATHING HEAVILY]

50
00:02:25,812 --> 00:02:27,105
Mommy! Mommy!

51
00:02:27,188 --> 00:02:28,982
Mommy, wake up!

52
00:02:29,607 --> 00:02:31,609
Wake up, Mommy!

53
00:02:31,693 --> 00:02:34,654
Mommy! Mommy!

54
00:02:34,737 --> 00:02:36,990
[FIRE ALARM BEEPING]

55
00:02:37,073 --> 00:02:40,076
Help! Help!

56
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:56,259
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

57
00:03:25,872 --> 00:03:30,710
[MIKE COUGHING]

58
00:03:30,793 --> 00:03:31,836
[GROANS]

59
00:03:33,546 --> 00:03:37,008
[GROANING, COUGHING]

60
00:03:37,091 --> 00:03:39,844
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

61
00:03:39,928 --> 00:03:40,803
[MIKE] Honey?

62
00:03:40,887 --> 00:03:42,972
Honey!

63
00:03:43,056 --> 00:03:45,141
[MIKE GROANING]

64
00:03:45,225 --> 00:03:49,187
Minnie! Minnie… Minnie! Minnie.

65
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:52,357
Hon? [GROANS IN PAIN]
What happened to you?

66
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:55,401
[FIRE ALARM BEEPING]

67
00:03:55,485 --> 00:03:56,486
Let's go.

68
00:03:56,569 --> 00:03:58,154
Where's Maddie?

69
00:03:58,238 --> 00:03:59,822
- Maddie…
- Where's Maddie?

70
00:03:59,906 --> 00:04:02,492
I don't know.
We were together just before.

71
00:04:02,575 --> 00:04:04,577
Huh? Wait.

72
00:04:04,661 --> 00:04:06,412
We have to find Maddie!

73
00:04:06,496 --> 00:04:08,539
- [MIKE] Maddie!
- [MINNIE] Maddie!

74
00:04:09,499 --> 00:04:11,000
- [MIKE GRUNTS]
- [AREZA] Come on.

75
00:04:11,084 --> 00:04:12,335
[MIKE] Let's go.

76
00:04:12,418 --> 00:04:13,461
Maddie!

77
00:04:13,544 --> 00:04:15,922
- Maddie!
- Maddie!

78
00:04:16,005 --> 00:04:21,219
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

79
00:04:21,302 --> 00:04:22,971
[COUGHS]

80
00:04:23,054 --> 00:04:26,724
Help us, please! Help! [COUGHS]

81
00:04:26,808 --> 00:04:28,643
Help us!

82
00:04:28,726 --> 00:04:30,979
[COUGHING]

83
00:04:32,814 --> 00:04:34,899
- Liam!
- Maddie!

84
00:04:36,901 --> 00:04:37,944
[MADDIE COUGHS]

85
00:04:38,027 --> 00:04:44,158
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

86
00:04:47,078 --> 00:04:48,121
I'm here, Maddie.

87
00:04:48,204 --> 00:04:50,540
[MADDIE COUGHING]

88
00:04:51,374 --> 00:04:52,458
Ma!

89
00:04:54,002 --> 00:04:55,003
Ma!

90
00:04:58,006 --> 00:04:59,841
- [LIAM COUGHING]
- [MADDIE CRYING]

91
00:04:59,924 --> 00:05:06,806
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

92
00:05:06,889 --> 00:05:08,224
[COUGHING]

93
00:05:08,308 --> 00:05:13,479
Mommy. Mommy.
[COUGHS]

94
00:05:17,233 --> 00:05:21,487
[COUGHING]

95
00:05:21,571 --> 00:05:24,866
[HOMER] Lucas, go help
Boss Emil. Help him!

96
00:05:24,949 --> 00:05:31,956
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

97
00:05:35,918 --> 00:05:37,086
[EXPLOSION]

98
00:05:40,048 --> 00:05:41,841
[FIRE HISSES]

99
00:05:41,924 --> 00:05:44,177
[LUCAS] Boss! Boss Emil!

100
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:47,597
- Boss! Boss Emil!
- Boss!

101
00:05:49,098 --> 00:05:52,143
Lucas, get Leni!

102
00:05:52,769 --> 00:05:54,395
[LUCAS SCREAMING] Boss!

103
00:05:54,479 --> 00:05:55,897
No, Homer!

104
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,940
Boss! Boss!

105
00:05:58,024 --> 00:05:59,567
[TUNNEL CRUMBLING]

106
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:03,196
[LUCAS] Boss! Boss! Boss!

107
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:05,073
[TUNNEL CRUMBLING]

108
00:06:05,156 --> 00:06:07,200
Boss!

109
00:06:07,283 --> 00:06:09,619
Boss!

110
00:06:09,702 --> 00:06:11,913
[CONCRETE CRASHES]

111
00:06:11,996 --> 00:06:13,831
- [EMIL] Get Leni!
- [LUCAS] Boss! Boss!

112
00:06:13,915 --> 00:06:15,958
Boss!

113
00:06:16,042 --> 00:06:19,170
Boss! Boss!

114
00:06:19,253 --> 00:06:25,468
[STIRRING MUSIC CONTINUES]

115
00:06:28,262 --> 00:06:29,514
[MUSIC TURNS DRAMATIC]

116
00:06:29,597 --> 00:06:36,604
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

117
00:06:42,652 --> 00:06:45,863
[MADDIE COUGHING]

118
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:50,701
[MADDIE COUGHING]

119
00:06:50,785 --> 00:06:56,958
[PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING]

120
00:06:58,709 --> 00:07:01,170
[AYEN] <i>Magnus, you promised me.</i>

121
00:07:01,254 --> 00:07:03,422
<i>You said you would break up with Greta!</i>

122
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:07,301
<i>That was a clear promise.</i>
<i>Why haven't you done it yet?</i>

123
00:07:07,885 --> 00:07:14,767
[PENSIVE MUSIC CONTINUES]

124
00:07:14,851 --> 00:07:17,478
<i>- Ayen, it's not as easy as--</i>
<i>- Why not?</i>

125
00:07:17,562 --> 00:07:21,149
<i>You just have to tell her</i>
<i>there'll be another Roja!</i>

126
00:07:21,232 --> 00:07:24,444
<i>That there's another one</i>
<i>besides Liam! That's all!</i>

127
00:07:24,527 --> 00:07:29,407
[PENSIVE MUSIC CONTINUES]

128
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,741
<i>I'm sorry, but…</i>

129
00:07:31,909 --> 00:07:33,536
<i>I still have to make sure.</i>

130
00:07:35,663 --> 00:07:37,582
<i>Make sure of what?</i>

131
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:40,835
<i>Make sure of what, Magnus?</i>

132
00:07:41,627 --> 00:07:44,088
<i>What do you need to make sure of, huh?</i>

133
00:07:44,172 --> 00:07:47,008
<i>If you really are the father of my child?!</i>

134
00:07:47,091 --> 00:07:49,510
<i>Is that it?! Magnus, you're shameless!</i>

135
00:07:49,594 --> 00:07:51,721
<i>You're even doubting me now!</i>

136
00:07:51,804 --> 00:07:54,390
- [GROANS]
<i>- Hey.</i>

137
00:07:54,474 --> 00:07:56,017
<i>Take it easy.</i>

138
00:07:59,937 --> 00:08:02,732
[GROANS, PANTING]

139
00:08:02,815 --> 00:08:05,026
<i>Why would you say that to me?</i>

140
00:08:08,905 --> 00:08:11,991
<i>I don't even beg for your love anymore.</i>

141
00:08:14,076 --> 00:08:15,828
<i>And now you're saying that?</i>

142
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:20,917
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

143
00:08:25,588 --> 00:08:29,217
<i>Okay? Okay. Okay. I'm sorry.</i>

144
00:08:30,426 --> 00:08:31,761
[MAGNUS SIGHS DEEPLY]

145
00:08:33,763 --> 00:08:34,972
<i>We're gonna be okay.</i>

146
00:08:35,056 --> 00:08:42,063
[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

147
00:08:42,647 --> 00:08:43,648
[FIRE HISSING]

148
00:08:43,731 --> 00:08:48,277
[FIRE ALARM BEEPING]

149
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:57,078
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

150
00:08:57,161 --> 00:08:59,622
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

151
00:09:00,206 --> 00:09:01,624
<i>What are you doing here?</i>

152
00:09:04,752 --> 00:09:06,128
<i>How did you get in?</i>

153
00:09:06,212 --> 00:09:10,383
[OMINOUS MUSIC CONTINUES]

154
00:09:10,466 --> 00:09:11,926
[GRETA SCREAMS FURIOUSLY]

155
00:09:12,009 --> 00:09:16,764
[MUSIC TURNS TENSE]

156
00:09:16,847 --> 00:09:17,890
<i>That's it?</i>

157
00:09:20,685 --> 00:09:22,270
<i>Go ahead, Greta.</i>

158
00:09:22,353 --> 00:09:24,855
<i>Destroy everything you want to destroy.</i>

159
00:09:24,939 --> 00:09:27,275
<i>Magnus will just replace it</i>
<i>with something new anyway.</i>

160
00:09:28,609 --> 00:09:30,736
<i>Everything can be replaced.</i>

161
00:09:31,654 --> 00:09:32,822
<i>Even you.</i>

162
00:09:36,784 --> 00:09:38,744
<i>Do you really know Magnus?</i>

163
00:09:39,662 --> 00:09:42,123
<i>My husband will eventually</i>
<i>lose interest in you.</i>

164
00:09:42,206 --> 00:09:43,791
<i>He'll surely replace you.</i>

165
00:09:43,874 --> 00:09:46,460
<i>In the end, he'll come back to me.</i>

166
00:09:47,878 --> 00:09:48,921
<i>Really?</i>

167
00:09:51,299 --> 00:09:54,677
<i>Then why are you wasting your time on me?</i>

168
00:09:56,304 --> 00:09:59,098
- [ENVELOPE THUDS]
- [PAPERS RUSTLE]

169
00:09:59,181 --> 00:10:02,268
<i>Because it turns out</i>
<i>it's not just my husband that you stole.</i>

170
00:10:02,351 --> 00:10:07,398
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

171
00:10:07,481 --> 00:10:08,608
[AYEN SCOFFS]

172
00:10:13,988 --> 00:10:15,156
<i>Okay, Greta.</i>

173
00:10:17,283 --> 00:10:18,909
<i>Before Magnus and I got together,</i>

174
00:10:18,993 --> 00:10:22,622
<i>didn't you convince me</i>
<i>to release company funds?</i>

175
00:10:24,624 --> 00:10:26,792
<i>Were you the only one</i>
<i>meant to benefit from that?</i>

176
00:10:27,918 --> 00:10:29,920
<i>The money I took</i>

177
00:10:30,004 --> 00:10:35,426
<i>was my service fee</i>
<i>for manipulating your finances</i>

178
00:10:35,509 --> 00:10:38,346
<i>so you could fund your gambling!</i>

179
00:10:38,429 --> 00:10:40,890
<i>You'll pay for this!</i>

180
00:10:41,557 --> 00:10:42,892
<i>Go on. Try me.</i>

181
00:10:45,186 --> 00:10:47,355
<i>Let's see if Magnus believes you.</i>

182
00:10:48,397 --> 00:10:50,107
<i>Are you trying to blackmail me?</i>

183
00:10:50,816 --> 00:10:52,151
[GRETA SCOFFS]

184
00:10:52,234 --> 00:10:55,363
<i>I will turn the tables.</i>

185
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:58,699
<i>I'll tell him you're the one who stole it.</i>

186
00:10:59,575 --> 00:11:01,744
<i>Let's see if he believes you.</i>

187
00:11:03,412 --> 00:11:04,580
[SCOFFS]

188
00:11:05,289 --> 00:11:07,958
<i>Especially now, Greta,</i>

189
00:11:09,293 --> 00:11:12,129
<i>when he already knows</i>
<i>he's about to be a father again.</i>

190
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:15,216
[AYEN SCOFFS]

191
00:11:17,676 --> 00:11:18,886
<i>Yes, Greta.</i>

192
00:11:19,762 --> 00:11:21,013
<i>I'm pregnant.</i>

193
00:11:21,847 --> 00:11:23,682
<i>And Magnus is the father.</i>

194
00:11:24,725 --> 00:11:25,976
- [GRETA GRUNTS]
- [SLAP LANDS]

195
00:11:27,978 --> 00:11:29,313
- [AYEN GRUNTS]
- [GRETA GROANS]

196
00:11:29,897 --> 00:11:32,149
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

197
00:11:32,233 --> 00:11:34,568
- You witch!
- [AYEN SCREAMS]

198
00:11:36,612 --> 00:11:41,158
- [ALARM BLARING]
- [DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

199
00:11:41,242 --> 00:11:42,785
[AMBULANCE SIREN WAILING]

200
00:11:42,868 --> 00:11:48,374
[ALARM BLARING]

201
00:11:48,457 --> 00:11:50,042
The firefighters are here.

202
00:11:54,588 --> 00:12:00,803
[POLICEMEN] Medic! Medic!

203
00:12:00,886 --> 00:12:05,683
[DRAMATIC MUSIC INTENSIFIES]

204
00:12:05,766 --> 00:12:07,643
- [POLICE] You can't go there, sir!
- [OLSEN] Liam!

205
00:12:07,726 --> 00:12:09,186
[LIAM GRUNTS]

206
00:12:10,688 --> 00:12:14,984
- He's with us! Liam! Liam!
- [POLICEMEN] Medic!

207
00:12:15,734 --> 00:12:17,153
[ICE] Liam!

208
00:12:17,236 --> 00:12:19,113
- Medic!
- [LUNA] Liam!

209
00:12:24,243 --> 00:12:26,620
- [OLSEN] Is he okay?
- [MEDIC] Over here.

210
00:12:26,704 --> 00:12:28,622
- [GRUNTS]
- Doc…

211
00:12:28,706 --> 00:12:30,791
- Put him on the stretcher.
- Liam!

212
00:12:30,875 --> 00:12:36,922
- [DRAMATIC MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [AMBULANCE SIREN WAILING]

213
00:12:37,923 --> 00:12:38,924
[OLSEN GRUNTS]

214
00:12:39,008 --> 00:12:41,927
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

215
00:12:42,011 --> 00:12:44,263
- [OLSEN PANTING]
- [DOCTOR] Okay, ready.

216
00:12:53,647 --> 00:12:56,734
- [MEDIC] One, two, three, up!
- [OLSEN GRUNTING]

217
00:12:56,817 --> 00:12:58,068
[LUNA] Liam!

218
00:12:59,153 --> 00:13:00,112
[OLSEN] Bro.

219
00:13:00,196 --> 00:13:05,784
[STRETCHER CLINKING]

220
00:13:05,868 --> 00:13:12,625
[SORROWFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

221
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:33,521
- [AMBULANCE SIREN WAILING]
- [CAR ENGINE REVVING]

222
00:13:33,604 --> 00:13:40,569
[SORROWFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

223
00:13:45,157 --> 00:13:51,914
- [FIRE CRACKLING]
- [EERIE MUSIC PLAYING]

224
00:14:05,803 --> 00:14:08,097
[EERIE MUSIC CONTINUES]

225
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:09,682
[AMBULANCE SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE]

226
00:14:09,765 --> 00:14:13,018
[SOBBING]

227
00:14:13,102 --> 00:14:14,478
Papa.

228
00:14:15,479 --> 00:14:17,064
We need to go back for Papa!

229
00:14:17,147 --> 00:14:18,357
He's gone.

230
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:20,609
[CRYING]

231
00:14:20,693 --> 00:14:22,570
He's gone already.

232
00:14:23,821 --> 00:14:25,197
[GROANS]

233
00:14:27,116 --> 00:14:28,868
We have to go back for him!

234
00:14:28,951 --> 00:14:30,369
Seriously?

235
00:14:32,079 --> 00:14:33,831
- [CRYING]
- [GWEN] Boss Emil is gone.

236
00:14:33,914 --> 00:14:34,832
No!

237
00:14:34,915 --> 00:14:36,041
He's gone.

238
00:14:36,125 --> 00:14:40,045
[GRIM MUSIC PLAYING]

239
00:14:40,129 --> 00:14:42,423
He's buried under the building.

240
00:14:44,133 --> 00:14:46,343
We don't know where he could be.

241
00:14:48,429 --> 00:14:52,182
We won't be able to find him
even if we go back.

242
00:14:52,266 --> 00:14:55,144
[GRIM MUSIC CONTINUES]

243
00:14:55,227 --> 00:14:57,021
I told you, he's gone!

244
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:07,323
[LENI CRYING]

245
00:15:11,452 --> 00:15:13,287
[HISSING]

246
00:15:13,370 --> 00:15:17,917
[SCREAMING IN FURY]

247
00:15:23,422 --> 00:15:24,590
[THUDS]

248
00:15:26,592 --> 00:15:27,927
[CRIES]

249
00:15:30,304 --> 00:15:34,475
[OLSEN] Sir, they just checked
us at the triage.

250
00:15:34,558 --> 00:15:36,894
[INDISTINCT MURMURING]

251
00:15:36,977 --> 00:15:38,646
[OLSEN] Move aside!

252
00:15:38,729 --> 00:15:44,902
- [FIRE TRUCK SIREN WAILING]
- [POLICE 1] Move aside!

253
00:15:49,239 --> 00:15:55,329
[AMBULANCE SIREN WAILING]

254
00:15:57,581 --> 00:15:58,874
[OLSEN] Carry the child inside!

255
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:06,966
[CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING]

256
00:16:12,471 --> 00:16:14,223
- [MEDIC] Exhale.
- [EXHALES]

257
00:16:15,182 --> 00:16:16,350
[MEDIC] Does it hurt?

258
00:16:16,433 --> 00:16:17,643
No. [SNIFFLES]

259
00:16:18,227 --> 00:16:25,192
[MIKE AND MINNIE
COUGHING STRENUOUSLY]

260
00:16:28,737 --> 00:16:32,866
[BOTH WHEEZING]

261
00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:35,911
- Medic! Medic!
- Medic!

262
00:16:35,995 --> 00:16:37,788
[MIKE] My wife's a cancer patient.

263
00:16:37,871 --> 00:16:40,624
- Please help her instead.
- [MINNIE] No! No! No!

264
00:16:40,708 --> 00:16:42,710
- I'm going to look for Maddie!
- Stay here, please.

265
00:16:42,793 --> 00:16:44,920
- Hon, I'll go look for her.
- No!

266
00:16:45,004 --> 00:16:47,381
- Please, assist her.
- [CRYING] Where's Maddie?

267
00:16:47,464 --> 00:16:48,382
[MIKE] Let's go!

268
00:16:48,465 --> 00:16:49,925
- Mommy!
- [MINNIE] Maddie!

269
00:16:51,427 --> 00:16:52,594
Mommy! Daddy!

270
00:16:53,971 --> 00:16:55,139
Maddie!

271
00:16:57,474 --> 00:16:59,977
- [MINNIE, MUFFLED] Maddie, my dear.
- [MIKE] Maddie.

272
00:17:00,060 --> 00:17:06,567
[EMOTIONAL MUSIC PLAYING]

273
00:17:17,745 --> 00:17:23,917
[FIRE CRACKLING]

274
00:17:38,932 --> 00:17:45,898
- [FIRE CRACKLING]
- [STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

275
00:17:46,982 --> 00:17:53,072
[FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]

276
00:18:01,371 --> 00:18:03,624
<i>…you were involved in that drug operation.</i>

277
00:18:08,337 --> 00:18:09,922
<i>What's this?</i>

278
00:18:11,381 --> 00:18:14,134
<i>- Huh? What's that?</i>
- [AYEN SLIGHTLY GROANS]

279
00:18:14,218 --> 00:18:18,138
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

280
00:18:18,222 --> 00:18:19,556
<i>What's that?</i>

281
00:18:20,557 --> 00:18:23,268
<i>- Who did that to you?</i>
<i>- It's nothing, Pa.</i>

282
00:18:24,728 --> 00:18:26,939
<i>Is Magnus hurting you?</i>

283
00:18:27,815 --> 00:18:28,774
[PUFFS]

284
00:18:28,857 --> 00:18:30,400
<i>No, Papa.</i>

285
00:18:30,484 --> 00:18:32,444
<i>How many times has this happened?</i>

286
00:18:34,196 --> 00:18:37,324
- [SUSPENSEFUL STING]
- [INHALES SHARPLY]

287
00:18:41,954 --> 00:18:45,124
[SINISTER MUSIC PLAYING]

288
00:18:50,838 --> 00:18:54,258
<i>Check the area carefully,</i>
<i>including the sewage system.</i>

289
00:18:54,341 --> 00:18:55,884
<i>Focus on Marcelino Street.</i>

290
00:18:55,968 --> 00:19:00,347
<i>According to Engineer Mike,</i>
<i>the hostage takers will exit from there!</i>

291
00:19:02,683 --> 00:19:05,227
<i>Where's Ma'am Greta?</i>
<i>Did they find her or not?</i>

292
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,436
<i>Did she make it out?</i>

293
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:08,021
[OFFICER] <i>Emil Padua</i>
<i>has been found.</i>

294
00:19:10,023 --> 00:19:11,233
<i>Do you know anything?</i>

295
00:19:11,316 --> 00:19:13,360
<i>Is it true your mom was involved?</i>

296
00:19:13,443 --> 00:19:18,115
<i>Shouldn't you be focusing more on catching</i>
<i>Lucas Sebastian and his associates?</i>

297
00:19:18,198 --> 00:19:21,952
<i>What if they're already holding her</i>
<i>hostage right now, as we speak?</i>

298
00:19:22,035 --> 00:19:25,164
<i>If I find out where my wife is hiding,</i>

299
00:19:25,247 --> 00:19:27,374
<i>I will surrender her to you myself.</i>

300
00:19:28,292 --> 00:19:30,252
<i>I'm just thinking about Mama.</i>

301
00:19:30,335 --> 00:19:33,589
<i>Wherever she is,</i>
<i>I just know that she's not safe.</i>

302
00:19:33,672 --> 00:19:34,882
<i>So I hope she surrenders.</i>

303
00:19:34,965 --> 00:19:37,718
[POLICE SIREN WAILING]

304
00:19:40,637 --> 00:19:43,015
<i>I'm glad you've found your purpose.</i>

305
00:19:44,057 --> 00:19:47,477
<i>Even if I'll be far away?</i>

306
00:19:49,521 --> 00:19:51,315
[LUCAS] <i>The mission is not over yet.</i>

307
00:19:51,398 --> 00:19:54,860
<i>We need to get Boss Emil.</i>
<i>We need to get Mila!</i>

308
00:19:54,943 --> 00:19:59,239
[REPORTER] <i>The leader of the group,</i>
<i>Emil Padua, is in critical condition.</i>

309
00:19:59,323 --> 00:20:01,116
[LUNA] <i>Why did you even volunteer?</i>

310
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:03,869
<i>Why do you have to treat Emil Padua?</i>

311
00:20:03,952 --> 00:20:06,914
<i>Until all of them are caught,</i>
<i>we are not safe.</i>

312
00:20:07,497 --> 00:20:11,084
<i>I understand</i>
<i>where your loyalty is, Magnus.</i>

313
00:20:11,668 --> 00:20:13,295
<i>But what about my father?</i>

314
00:20:14,129 --> 00:20:17,424
<i>What about the people who suffered</i>
<i>because of your wife?</i>

315
00:20:20,219 --> 00:20:21,720
[AREZA] <i>I believe you are innocent.</i>

316
00:20:21,803 --> 00:20:23,263
[WOMAN] <i>Put the Rojas behind bars!</i>

317
00:20:23,347 --> 00:20:25,766
[PROTESTORS]
<i>Put the Rojas behind bars!</i>

318
00:20:25,849 --> 00:20:29,811
- [PROTESTOR 1] <i>They shouldn't be free!</i>
- [PROTESTOR 2] <i>Criminals!</i>

319
00:20:30,562 --> 00:20:37,486
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
